  <title>Unit Summary 2b Loops (2.7-2.12)</title><introduction>
    
    <p>In the second half of this unit, lessons 2.7-2.12, you learned about <term>loops</term>.  <term>Loops</term> are used to repeat a statement or block of statements inside a pair of curly braces.</p>
